reviews:
Pros:
Material stretches very well.
Colours are vibrant; really nice.
Material is cool and comfortable to wear.
Cons:
Sizing is definitely on the small side.
Waist fits small so it’s very snug if you have a belly.
Material is also thin and reveals your body (like chest hair and belly).

So if you’ve got a great body, this is the shirt for you! If however your carrying a little extra weight, this shirt will also show it off :)
